	<div id="content" class="page-container container" style="padding-top:22px">
		<header class="header">
			
			<h1 class="title" align="left">
				【漳州】东山岛腌虾姑，吃过一次就终身上瘾！
			</h1>
			<div class="desc">
				<img src="//om.gtimg.cn/om/om_3.0/h5_detail/images/logo_qiehao.png" class="logo">
				<span class="author">福建旅游</span>
				<span class="date">2019-11-20</span>
			</div>
			
		</header>
		<section class="article">
			

			

			
		
			
				
					
						<p>若问一个外地人，</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>在东山岛，考验海鲜是否新鲜</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>该用什么做法？</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>他大概会告诉你<strong>白灼</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/10803516106/0" width="100%" style="display:block;"
					data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/10803516106/0">
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>但其实，</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>在东山岛还有另一种做法</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>能和白灼媲美</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>那就是<strong>生腌</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p><strong>尤其是生腌虾姑</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>简直是东山人的最爱</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516107/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516107/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>最近天气渐冷</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>虾姑越来越肥美了</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p><strong>地瓜粥的粥铺</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p><strong>和铜陵镇的街头</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>又开始出现了腌虾姑的身影</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516109/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516109/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516110/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516110/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>这个时候</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>岛上的东山人想着</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>买点回家配地瓜粥</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>岛外的吃货</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>就只能默默抽张纸巾</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>擦擦口水</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516112/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/10803516112/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>腌虾姑最大程度上</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>保留了海鲜的鲜甜原味</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>鲜嫩可口，让人无法抗拒，</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>外地人也许会觉得重口味</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>无法理解这种吃法</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>但是一旦试过却会无可救药的上瘾</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>所以，答应我</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>如果来了一定要试看看！</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/10803516113/0" width="100%" style="display:block;"
					data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/10803516113/0">
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>你可以去店里、路边摊购买</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>也可以自己买来新鲜虾姑制作</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>如果你是出门在外的东山人</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p><strong>也不妨来看看腌虾姑怎么做</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p><strong>给自己做一份家乡味</strong></p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/5799236797/0" width="100%" style="display:block;"
					data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/5799236797/0">
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988455/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988455/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>1</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>购买新鲜虾蛄</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>洗干净后备用</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988394/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988394/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>2</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>蒜头，切碎后备用</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>蒜头的量是宁滥勿缺</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>有一种说法是两斤虾蛄一斤蒜头</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>蒜头能杀灭细菌</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>而且蒜香也是这道菜的重要特征</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988386/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988386/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>辣椒就因人而异，看个人喜好决定</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>6个左右，切尽量碎备用</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729028/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729028/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>香菜，洗干净备用</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>用刀拍一下，其他切碎片</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729030/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729030/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>洗净的虾蛄，加入白醋</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>白醋的作用是杀死寄生虫</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>防止肚子里长虫子，还有调味的功能</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>白醋和蒜头搭配的味道特别好</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729031/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729031/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729033/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729033/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>然后要把醋倒掉，不然太酸</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729035/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729035/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>加入生抽酱油</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>也可以用老抽，看个人口味</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>如果不想太盐，但生抽又不能少</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>那么可以加一点矿泉水或纯净水</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729036/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729036/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988411/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988411/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729029/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729029/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988379/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988379/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>将切成碎片的配料都加入</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>搅拌均匀</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729037/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795729037/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>然后盖上保鲜膜，放入冰箱冷藏间</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>大约4个小时后</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>就可以品尝这道生猛海鲜美味了</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988450/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/5795988450/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>来源 | 黄沙海鲜</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>温馨提示：海鲜过敏者不可食用。这道菜比较寒凉，肠胃功能不良的朋友，吃完容易拉稀。</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>当然，东山岛的生腌美食</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>还有这些</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>腌螃蟹</p>
					
				
			
				
					
						<p>▼</p>
					
				
			
				
